## Overview

Transform Calendar from basic month view with all-day events to a professional scheduling tool comparable to Google Calendar. Current parity: 45%. Target: 65-70%.

**Key Deliverables:**
1. Day view (hour-by-hour timeline)
2. Recurring events (daily, weekly, monthly)
3. Multi-day events
4. Event reminders (browser notifications)
5. Import/export .ics files
6. Agenda view (list format)
7. Conflict detection

