### Event Type Extension

**Current:**
```typescript
interface Event {
  id: string;
  title: string;
  date: string; // YYYY-MM-DD
  startTime?: string; // HH:MM
  endTime?: string; // HH:MM
  description?: string;
  category?: string;
  color?: string;
